..........................................26\n2.6. Award of Incremental TCCs .............................................................................................................26\n3. INTERCONNECTION PROCESS......................................................................................................................................27\n3.1. Introduction......................................................................................................................................27\n3.2. What is an Interconnection? ...........................................................................................................28\n3.3. Large Facility Interconnection Procedures (LFIP) ..........................................................................28\n3.3.1. Basic Information about the LFIP.....................................................................................................28\n3.3.2. Large Facility Interconnection Request............................................................................................32\n3.3.3. Basic Steps of the LFIP......................................................................................................................33\n3.3.4. Materiality Determinations .............................................................................................................53\n3.4. Small Generator Interconnection Procedures (SGIP)....................................................................59\n3.4.1. Basic Information about the SGIP ....................................................................................................59\n3.4.2. Small Generator Interconnection Request.......................................................................................61\n3.4.3. Basic Steps of the SGIP.....................................................................................................................62\n3.4.4. Small Generator Interconnection Studies ........................................................................................62\n3.4.5. Small Generator Intercon",
